## Common Tasks

### Add New Project
1. Create Blade template in `resources/views/projects/{name}/index.blade.php`
2. Add entry to ProjectSeeder.php
3. Update ProjectController::show() method
4. Test responsive design

### Backend Changes
1. Follow Laravel conventions
2. Use Eloquent relationships
3. Implement proper validation
4. Add error handling

